BuildBuddy AI – Real-Time AI Coding Mentor (MCP Enabled)
1. Product Positioning
Category
AI-Powered Developer Education Platform (Context-Aware via MCP)
Tagline
“AI that doesn’t just answer — it teaches.”
Core Differentiator
Unlike ChatGPT-style assistants, BuildBuddy:
Analyzes real user code
Explains WHY errors occur
Gives structured step-by-step fixes
Acts as a contextual coding mentor
Uses persistent memory via MCP
Adapts explanations based on past mistakes
