5. API Design (With MCP)
POST /analyze-code
Input:
{
  language,
  code,
  project_id
}
Now backend:
Loads context from MCP
Analyzes code
Injects relevant memory
Returns structured JSON
GET /history
Now context-aware filtering supported.
POST /save-session
Stores:
Code
AI response
Memory updates
